    <p class="scroll-animation scroll-animation-default delay-1000 text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl italic mt-2.5">"Don't work hard, work smart" - Allen F. Morgenstern</p>
    <div class="scroll-animation scroll-animation-default flex space-x-5 mt-4">
      <Icons class="lg:h-10 lg:w-10 sm:h-8 sm:w-8 h-6 w-6"/>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>